<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Numbers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Registration Numbers</h1>
        <div class="menu">
            <form action="/add" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="regNumInput" id="">
                <button id="addBtn" type="submit">Add</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/filter" method="POST">
                <div class="filter-section">
                    <select name="townSelect" id="towns">
                        <option value="default">Select a town</option>
                        <option value="ca">Cape Town (CA)</option>
                        <option value="cj">Paarl (CJ)</option>
                        <option value="caw">George (CAW)</option>
                        <option value="cl">Stellenbosch (CL)</option>
                        <option value="cy">Bellville (CY)</option>
                    </select>
                    <button id="filterBtn" type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>
            <form action="/showAll" method="POST">
                <button id="showAllBtn">Show All</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/deleteAll" method="POST">
                <button id="clearBtn" type="submit">Clear Data</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div
            class="errorOrInfoDisplay {{#if messages.error}}errorStyle{{else}}{{#if messages.success}}successStyle{{/if}}{{/if}}">
            {{#if messages.error}}
            {{{messages.error}}}
            {{else}}
            {{#if messages.success}}
            {{{messages.success}}}
            {{/if}}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="displayArea">
            {{#unless regNumsList}}
            <div>
                <p>Why so empty !?? üßê</p>
                <p> Add some registration numbers to get started</p>
            </div>
            {{/unless}}
            <ul>
                {{#each regNumsList}}
                <li>{{this}}<span>x</span></li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </div>
        <section class="modal hidden modalFadeIn">
            <h3>Welcome to the Registration Numbers App!<span>x</span></h3>
            <div>
                <p><strong>Let me introduce you to some of the basic features available to use:</strong></p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> You can add a registration number plate by entering a valid registration number
                <p><strong>*</strong> The following areas are supported: Cape Town (CA), Paarl (CJ), George (CAW),
                    Stellenbosch (CL) and Bellvile (CY)</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> Valid registration numbers are in the format of: 2 capital alphabet characters,
                    followed by a space, and 3-5 numbers afterwards</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> There are notifications for any user mistakes or errors you may make</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> You have the ability to filter results by area using the drop down menu</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> After filtering click the Show All button to show all registration numbers</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> Registration numbers may be deleted individually by hovering over the individual
                    registration number and clicking the close button</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> Registration numbers are persisted to the database and available upon refreshing
                    the page</p>
                <p><strong>*</strong> There is a limit imposed of 15 registration numbers that can be added at a time to
                    accomodate the space available to display them</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <div class="overlay hidden"></div>
    </div>
    <script src="/registration-numbers.js"></script>
</body>

</html>